Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是我的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的扭曲點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們要用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.15,0:23:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將世界的扭曲破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的發展型？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arche Gundam：權天使高達，Throne系列的發展型）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這就開戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之間盛大的戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被回憶束縛  看不到未來的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們所思如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「無法逝去的過去」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.72,0:24:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使明天  覺醒時也已成回憶


